Tables and configuration are set in the database. 
Exporting these means they will be persisted. 

https://hasura.io/docs/1.0/graphql/manual/migrations/reference/how-it-works.html

- Download the hasura cli tool and copy it to a working folder
- Open CMD as Administrator
- `cli-hasura-windows-amd64.exe init`
- `cd hasura`
- `..\cli-hasura-windows-amd64.exe metadata export --admin-secret somesecretkey`